{"id": 1657, "genre": 1001, "title": "在这个浮夸的世界，你的家乡宣传语跟你的实际印象有什么出入？", "description": "这年头每个家乡都是物华天宝人杰地灵的，但你明明就觉得……蛤？（题图来自：林小妖）", "record_count": 2426, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170427150235EpK6eNPJjI8qd29f.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-04-28T03:00:44Z", "options": [{"id": 197888, "content": "四面荷花三面柳-_-#，柳树没有杨树多，荷花只有大明湖里有", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 980131}, {"id": 197889, "content": "成都，都成！", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1017687}, {"id": 197890, "content": "都只是一些面朝黄土背朝天的人啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1013796}, {"id": 199426, "content": "一座人人称“道”的城市——就因为有个武当山，全变道士道姑了......我道你妹", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 496901}, {"id": 197891, "content": "碧水鲜花阳光城", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 913343}, {"id": 197892, "content": "大美龙江，冰城夏都，东方小巴黎，冰天雪地也是金山银山", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1017694}, {"id": 197894, "content": "杭州，住在天堂，现在怎么感觉怪怪的……", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 916500}, {"id": 197895, "content": "中国科技城……然而科学城和绵阳小百姓没半毛钱关系", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 735592}, {"id": 199943, "content": "网络时代?只需一部手机?就多一份收入，多一份任性?微信咨询2227887341?每天至少50-300+，上不封顶，半月轻松入2000+?你不比别人差❗️差别就在于你缺少一个有实力的团队和一颗赚钱的心❤️", "image": "img/option/option/20170503195645J0tCzI7r4oiKMfTm.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1022018}, {"id": 197896, "content": "听说我们这儿创业成功率很高哦?", "image": "img/option/option/20170428234209GvtZ1lpETR0deFyH", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 991288}, {"id": 201992, "content": "网络时代?只需一部手机?就多一份收入，多一份任性?微信咨询2227887341?每天至少50-300+，上不封顶，半月轻松入2000+?你不比别人差❗️差别就在于你缺少一个有实力的团队和一颗赚钱的心❤️", "image": "img/option/option/20170509081128KqM147ZpiVFPjOzx.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1027056}, {"id": 197897, "content": "天池有水怪，来吧老铁们", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1011784}, {"id": 197899, "content": "来了就是XX人\n？我是辐射变种了？", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 105318}, {"id": 198155, "content": "烟头不落地，城市更美丽？\n外地人以外我们这是吸毒重灾区吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 955508}, {"id": 197901, "content": "以前号称“钢城”，其实这个还是蛮贴切的，不过后来铁矿越来越少，钢厂也不好办了，开始发展旅游业，口号是“北方水城”", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 880391}, {"id": 197902, "content": "大大的孙吴，小小的哈尔滨。\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 487732}, {"id": 206862, "content": "巴西????????????????????????????", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 908163}, {"id": 197903, "content": "安徽南部的黄山还可以，不过江北淮北都来沾边，全省打徽文化旗号", "image": "img/option/option/20170429002642AVtqeNLFB6ycpT57.jpg", "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1017729}, {"id": 199183, "content": "我的家乡号称广东西部的西藏，貌似没有宣传口号", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1016973}, {"id": 197904, "content": "一座你来了就不想走的城市", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 265681}, {"id": 197905, "content": "为了创卫，把我爱吃的烧烤摊全收了!!!", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 102092}, {"id": 198673, "content": "太湖美 美就美在太湖水。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1018802}, {"id": 197906, "content": "只是秀给自己看，或是蒙别人而已。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 699564}, {"id": 197907, "content": "作为一个上海人，表示从来没听说过什么“做爱的上海人”这种家乡宣传标语。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 928322}, {"id": 197908, "content": "外乡人初到无锡来，第一印象肯定不是“一座充满温情和水的城市。”，我想大概是“甜，甜到忧伤”", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1017775}, {"id": 197909, "content": "就一个风景区花没多少，人道是挺多的，关键是整天就知道宣传这个风景区，无语了（＃－.－）", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1006563}, {"id": 198165, "content": "完全想不起来厦门的宣传语", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 878925}, {"id": 198423, "content": "遂宁，已在这里等了你2200年(๑• . •๑)", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1019391}, {"id": 197657, "content": "半城山半城水，直到看了重庆才知道什么是真正的半城山半城水……", "image": null, "praise_count": 112, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 58260}, {"id": 197658, "content": "马踏飞燕…那个什么旅游城市和标志…不觉得有啥好旅游的…", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 492824}, {"id": 197914, "content": "九朝古都牡丹花城的那个我要来纠正一下是十三朝?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1000132}, {"id": 199194, "content": "爽爽的贵阳 ？？？？！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1020268}, {"id": 197661, "content": "罗定抗日英雄蔡廷锴", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 986031}, {"id": 197662, "content": "宣传什么我不知道...我只知道高考分最高", "image": null, "praise_count": 81, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 274087}, {"id": 197663, "content": "三皇五帝。。。商丘", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 554074}, {"id": 197664, "content": "号称国际化大都市，但其实只是一个大的城中村……", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1017211}, {"id": 197920, "content": "来东北体验奇葩", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1016915}, {"id": 197921, "content": "智慧新城，然而都是楼盘", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 935385}, {"id": 203553, "content": "“百年古镇，世界文化交点”，抬头看看破败不堪的骑楼，和满地的垃圾，感到羞愧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 764681}, {"id": 197666, "content": "食在广州，厨出凤城（顺德）。广州人都在吃电器吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 26, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 621968}, {"id": 197667, "content": "总有一条仿古街，打着不同的名义卖着同样的烤鱿鱼，臭豆腐……", "image": null, "praise_count": 57, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 127181}, {"id": 197923, "content": "山水甲天下", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1016256}, {"id": 197668, "content": "总有一条所谓的仿古街，打着不同的文化旗号，卖着同样的烤鱿鱼，臭豆腐……", "image": null, "praise_count": 551, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 127181}, {"id": 197924, "content": "岳阳天下水，洞庭天下楼", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1017889}, {"id": 197925, "content": "天地之美美在黄山，人生有梦梦圆徽州。没出入、没毛病～", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1017905}, {"id": 197670, "content": "人间天堂…完全不觉得", "image": "img/option/option/20170428112152FVqsexrvgDUPLHw4.jpg", "praise_count": 31, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 642016}, {"id": 197926, "content": "广州，美在花城", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 277107}, {"id": 197927, "content": "武汉，每天不一样。然后每天天气各种变！蜜汁尴尬。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 865541}, {"id": 197672, "content": "不知道家乡有什么宣传语哎。，就很尴尬", "image": null, "praise_count": 61, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688589}, {"id": 197928, "content": "烟花三月下扬州，然而并没有烟花了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1008472}]}